 increases. The lifetime for the stage with the strong Poynting\nflux is $1$-2 s, which agrees with the typical duration of short-hard gamma-ray\nbursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Nov 2021 16:48:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2023 13:36:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-27"}
