tion named Adaptive LDP for LOngitudinal and Multidimensional\nFREquency Estimates (ALLOMFREE), which randomly samples a single attribute to\nbe sent with the whole privacy budget and adaptively selects the optimal\nprotocol, i.e., either L-GRR or L-OSUE. As shown in the results, ALLOMFREE\nconsistently and considerably outperforms the state-of-the-art L-SUE and L-OUE\nprotocols in the quality of the frequency estimates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Nov 2021 17:04:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Jul 2022 08:11:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 16 Jul 2022 16:35:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-19"}
