 purely dataset-constrained Behavioral Cloning performs\ncompetitively to the best Offline RL algorithms for datasets with high TQ.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Nov 2021 18:48:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2022 14:34:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-13"}
