dence on the\navailability of experimental data and could lead to aqueous thermodynamic\nmodels capable of estimating the values of solute and solvent activities,\nthermal and volumetric properties for a wide range of composition and\nconcentrations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Nov 2021 22:03:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-26"}
