orphically\nto some neighbourhood of the unions of $\\sigma$-lc centres with some $L^2$\nestimates. The proof does not rely on the techniques in the\nOhsawa--Takegoshi-type $L^2$ extension theorems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 08:57:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2022 11:50:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2022 08:08:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 3 Sep 2022 11:56:37 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2023 16:05:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-06"}
