al acceleration. A detailed analysis of\ndependence of jet variables upon various parameters like plasma composition,\nmagnetic pressure in the disc, luminosity, accretion rate, jet geometry and jet\nlaunching energy etc, is carried out.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 14:30:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-10"}
